  "data": [
    [
      [
        "NO"
      ],
      [
        "I think for a moment but ultimately nod. "
      ],
      [
        " It’s okay, [Fabian], thank you for all this candy."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] hugs me tightly and gives me a kiss on the cheek."
      ],
      [
        " Thank you… I am so happy, I can’t believe this. "
      ],
      [
        "[He] suddenly remembers something and takes out a bunch of pages from [his] backpack. "
      ],
      [
        " Before I forget, The teacher gave us this study guide to complete for tomorrow…"
      ],
      [
        "would you like to do it together?"
      ],
      [
        "I nod and agree. [Fabian] helps me stand up and head to my desk."
      ],
      [
        "My leg bumps into the chair and it hurts me a little bit."
      ],
      [
        " Ow!"
      ],
      [
        "In half a second, Helpie opens my door and peeks in. "
      ],
      [
        " I-Is everything alright [tn]? Are you okay? "
      ],
      [
        "I nod and look at [Fabian], he doesn’t seem very happy that Helpie is here"
      ],
      [
        " Yes! Everything is alright! I just bumped into my chair, haha."
      ],
      [
        "Actually Helpie, could you go to the robotics store and ask for a full maintenance?"
      ],
      [
        "I haven’t gotten you one since a long time ago! "
      ],
      [
        " You sure [tn]? They sometimes take up to 12 hours!"
      ],
      [
        " Yeah, please go. You really need one. "
      ],
      [
        "With that, Helpie nodded and closed the door, not before looking for one last time at [Fabian]."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] scoffed and sat me on the chair."
      ],
      [
        " Getting rid of Helpie was a good call! Ehem… now, let’s start. "
      ],
      [
        "We start with the first question, and keep a good pace."
      ],
      [
        "Time flies by as we answer questions, we can feel sparks fly between us."
      ],
      [
        "Our hands brush against each other, and we share some kisses here and there. "
      ],
      [
        "All that romance may have distracted us a little bit, but we managed to complete the guide in just a few hours."
      ],
      [
        "We both stretched and yawned after working so much."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] then looked at me and tilted [his] head. "
      ],
      [
        " So… what should we do now? "
      ],
      [
        "I look around and my eyes land on my console."
      ],
      [
        "That 's right! I haven’t gotten all the achievements, maybe Fabian can help me. "
      ],
      [
        " Hey, how about we play this game? I bet it could be fun! "
      ],
      [
        " Okay, I’ve played it a few times before, Let’s do this. "
      ],
      [
        "I turn on the console and we start playing."
      ],
      [
        "It is very fun at first, we get a couple achievements and we laugh."
      ],
      [
        "However, as we keep on playing, I sense that [Fabian] tenses up."
      ],
      [
        "Especially when I win the round, and not [him]."
      ],
      [
        "We play a couple times more, and I let [him] win some rounds."
      ],
      [
        "Which probably wasn’t the best, since it made [his] ego go up."
      ],
      [
        "Every time I let [him] win, [he] laughed and said I was a bot…"
      ],
      [
        "We were now in the last round, whoever got one point would win the round."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] pushed on the buttons with a lot of force,"
      ],
      [
        "I was sure my control would end with at least a little bit of damage after this."
      ],
      [
        "With a swift movement, I manage to score the final point and the match was over."
      ],
      [
        "I had won!"
      ],
      [
        "I exhale and rest my back on my chair."
      ],
      [
        " Whew… I can’t believe it. That was lucky."
      ],
      [
        "I look at [Fabian] and [he]’s trembling."
      ],
      [
        "Suddenly, [He] throws my control to the wall and it smashes into a lot of pieces."
      ],
      [
        "I just look at it dumbfounded."
      ],
      [
        " BULLSHIT!!! YOU’RE A CHEATER!!!"
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] is just fuming, and cursing me… over a video game."
      ]
    ],
